  "body": "## Issue\r\nThe [nightfall box](https://trufflesuite.com/boxes/nightfall/index.html) doesn't work!  I spent some time with this but decided to open an issue and see if it's obvious to anyone.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\nRun `truffle unbox nightfall`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\nIt should install dependencies successfully.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n```shell\r\nnpm ERR! code 1\r\nnpm ERR! git dep preparation failed\r\nnpm ERR! command /Users/kevinweaver/.nvm/versions/node/v14.18.0/bin/node /Users/kevinweaver/.nvm/versions/node/v14.18.0/li\r\nb/node_modules/npm/bin/npm-cli.js install --force --cache=/Users/kevinweaver/.npm --prefer-offline=false --prefer-online=f\r\nalse --offline=false --no-progress --no-save --no-audit --include=dev --include=peer --include=optional --no-package-lock-\r\nonly --no-dry-run\r\nnpm ERR! npm WARN using --force Recommended protections disabled.\r\nnpm ERR! npm ERR! code 1\r\nnpm ERR! npm ERR! The git reference could not be found\r\nnpm ERR! npm ERR! command git --no-replace-objects checkout 4.0\r\nnpm ERR! npm ERR! error: pathspec '4.0' did not match any file(s) known to git\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: \r\n* Ethereum client:\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): v5.4.16\r\n* node version (`node --version`):  v14.18.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 8.3.0\r\n",
